steps.name: Input search text and press Enter

Verify that the search result is correct
$("app-search-result ion-card-content app-service-link") should have(text "Future Accountability Engineer (oqnppzxc)")

$("app-service-widget") should have(text "I hate to break it to you, but what people call 'love' is just a chemical reaction that compels animals to breed. It hits hard Morty then it slowly fades leaving you stranded in a failing marriage. I did it. Your parents are going to do it. Break the cycle Morty, rise above, focus on science. May the wind under your wings bear you where the sun sails and the moon walks.")
